flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Precheck certificate for renewal]

    B -->|Precheck failed| P1[Fail End]
    B -->|Precheck passed / renewal required| C[Raise change request]

    C --> D[Implement change request]
    D --> E[Renew certificate]

    E -->|Renew success| F[Deploy certificate keystore to server]
    E -->|Renew failed| R1[Failure node<br/>Set status unsuccessful<br/>Add renew failure information]

    F -->|Keystore deploy success| G[Deploy certificate to IHS server]
    F -->|Keystore deploy failed| K1[Failure node<br/>Set status unsuccessful<br/>Add keystore deployment failure information]

    G -->|IHS deploy success| S1[Close change request as successful<br/>with success information]
    G -->|IHS deploy failed| I1[Failure node<br/>Set status unsuccessful<br/>Add IHS deployment failure information]

    %% Shared failure handling for renew + keystore failures
    R1 --> CF1[Close change request as unsuccessful]
    K1 --> CF1

    CF1 --> CF2[Raise incident]
    CF2 --> CF3[Update change request with incident details]
    CF3 --> CF4[Send failure notification]
    CF4 --> X1[End]

    %% IHS failure path with approval + retry
    I1 --> IC1[Close change request as unsuccessful]
    IC1 --> IC2[Raise incident]
    IC2 --> IC3[Update change request with incident details]
    IC3 --> A1[Approval gate]
    A1 --> A2[Retry failed IHS nodes]

    A2 -->|Retry success| A3[Close incident]
    A3 --> A4[Send success notification to team]
    A4 --> X2[End]

    A2 -->|Retry failure| A5[Send failure notification to team]
    A5 --> X3[End]

    %% Success path
    S1 --> S2[Send success notification]
    S2 --> X4[End]
